                                                                                                             DISCUSSION
                                                                                                             Typical assessor actions may include interviewing chief executive officers, chief information officers,
                                                                                                             senior information security officers, information owners, system and mission owners, system
                                                                                                             security officers, system security managers, personnel officers, human resource managers, network
                                                                                                             and system administrators, facilities managers, training officers, physical security officers, system
                                                                                                             operators, site managers, and users.




